c: 33
v: 53
t: "Ko onon yo …ďen gom…óim…ďe ! Wata on naatu ka cuu…ói Annabiijo on, si wanaa hara on nodda e √Īaametee, hara wanaa yo on habbito ko …ďenndi ka makko. Kono si on noddaa ma, naatee. Si on √Īaamii, sentee, hara on …óa…ď…ďaali haala. Anndon …óum moo…óon, hino lorraynoo Annabiijo on, kono o hersa (haalannde) on, Alla non …óalataa [yamirde] goonga. Si on lanndoto (suddii…ďe makko) …ďen haaju, lanndoree …ďe …ďaawo wirngallo: ko …óum moo…óon, …ďuri laa…ďannde …ďer…óe mon e …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe. Haananaa on nde lorroton Nulaa…óo Alla on, wanaa nde resoton suddii…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen …ďaawo makko, poomaa; pellet, wa…óugol mon …óum, wonii ko mawni ka Alla"